  "title": "A UFO moving sideways was spotted in Porto Alegre-RS [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/29/a-ufo-moving-sideways-was-spotted-in-porto-alegre-rs-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1aA",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 21st, 1996</strong>. Time: 22h40. Duration: 20 minutes. When walking on the street of his house in Porto Alegre, State of Rio Grande do Sul, a man observed an unidentified flying object moving sideways at a slow speed. According to the witness, who was with two more people, the UFO was at an altitude of approximately 10km. They could tell that the object was shaped like a &#8220;small dot, varying in red, green and orange&#8221;. The sighting was done &#8220;with the naked eye&#8221;, under good conditions of visibility and without photographs taken.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.425. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Porto Alegre, Estado do Rio Grande do Sul”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
